gn: center;\">2017-10-8 12:19am-10:19pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/feOuBG4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfeOuBG4.png&h=65c3d702&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hoDMFjU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhoDMFjU.png&h=11288f58&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(12)陳逸敏vs梁嘉琪(5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"ea37ef03e96901dc358a18256cd4cd2fad6f5756","tid":427802,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:20:53.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得undefined undefined<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程undefined undefined<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/391410/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃第一圈抽籤結果<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/390687\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/390687</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃分組賽抽籤結果"},{"pid":"724567bd1bd5fa63c8910938c535a1db0881ced4","tid":427802,"uid":27970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:43:10.000Z","msg":"票已投"},{"pid":"f67a10e94876291f559ad8cfb0858967353344c6","tid":427802,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>票已投</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=